### Chi-squared Test Results
- **Language vs Type:** 
  - Chi2 Statistic: 829.10, P-value: 3.38e-130, Degrees of Freedom: 70
- **Language vs Title:**

- **Type vs Title:**

The results of the chi-squared tests indicate significant relationships between the categorical features, suggesting that the `language`, `type`, and `title` features are interdependent.
